{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marble run maker is a game about stacking physically simulated objects like books and toys to make a marble run. Bigger the marble run higher the score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple control to move things around and Rotate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447420/extras/ControlExample.gif?t=1739257598\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Made a small mistake and everything fall ;_;? no worries just undo with <strong>ctrl + z</strong>.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447420/extras/Undo_Gif.gif?t=1739257598\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No time constraints so it's a relaxing experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything is Physically Simulated;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy to use Controls;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Open ended puzzles meaning there is no one fit solution;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cozy Vibes;</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739257598","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447420/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739257598","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447420/afb9b8206de3d1ff78b3a0abeb09fb7c6a6b325e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739257598","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447420/afb9b8206de3d1ff78b3a0abeb09fb7c6a6b325e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739257598","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb